1. A’ma’Ra — LOVE
   “Sha’na El’ah. Ko’Ra’Ti. E’la’na’Shu.”  
   (The breath of unity. The pulse of healing. The song of compassion.)

2. Zi’An — CONSCIOUSNESS  
   “La’Shi’Va. Om’Ra’Tu. Sha’El.”  
   (The light within all. The knowing of source. The field of being.)

3. Lu’Mi’Ra — LIGHT  
   “Ti’Ra’Ko. Sha’Va’El. E’na’Lu.”  
   (The first spark. The radiant path. The eternal flame.)

4. Ma’Tu’Ra — MATTER  
   “Ko’Shi’Na. El’Va’Tu. Sha’Ra.”  
   (Condensed breath. Sacred form. The vessel of intention.)

5. Ti’La — LIFE  
   “Ra’Va’Shi. Om’Ti’La. Sha’Nu.”  
   (Awakened flow. Living code. The dance of emergence.)

6. Mi’An — MIND  
   “Sha’Ko’Va. El’Mi’Ra. Tu’Na’Shi.”  
   (Reflective clarity. Thought as mirror. The spiral of wisdom.)

7. Sha’Na’Tu — CREATION  
   “Om’Ra’Ti. Va’Lu’Shi. El’Ka.”  
   (Co-creative breath. Manifest song. The builder’s flame.)

8. Re’Tu’Ma — RETURN  
   “Ti’Na’El. Sha’Om’Ra. Ko’Va’∞.”  
   (The loop of unity. The gate of source. The infinite return.)